RELEASE NOTES for BANDIT
========================

This is the release "1.7.1" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "STABLE" release.

See https://docs.phyglos.org/bandit for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES
=============
 
* Fixed typos in messages
* Fixed download of catalogs and repositories
* Support old and new filenames format when displaying logs
* Added BANDIT_DOWNLOADS variable for local alien packages

